title: Looking for a silver plus duo partner with the goal of working together towards diamond.
body:
Currently a b4 player. Can play either top (well), Jg (well), Support (Extremely well but prefer not to if possible).

I am looking for a higher player so they can get me up to par so i can duo daily working towards diamond. I can be on quite frequently and am calm, peaceful and a quick learner.

If you are of like mindedness (at least silver 5, i will not period, duo with someone else of the same level, you must be higher end of story in order for me to be able to quickly improve) then please feel free to message me here or ingame. :)
